00:57:25,319 --> 00:57:28,280
Can I at least give you an awkward hug?

743
00:57:47,007 --> 00:57:49,801
- So, how are you feeling?
- I feel fine.

744
00:57:49,885 --> 00:57:53,055
Yeah? No dizziness,
disorientation, sleepiness?

745
00:57:53,138 --> 00:57:54,973
- Nope.
- Great.

746
00:57:55,057 --> 00:57:58,018
Well, I'm very happy,
and your CT scan looks excellent.

747
00:57:59,019 --> 00:58:00,729
What a relief. Well...

748
00:58:00,854 --> 00:58:03,732
So, your memory recall, anything?

749
00:58:03,815 --> 00:58:06,401
- Not really.
