All right, take it easy.

800
01:01:00,700 --> 01:01:02,577
- The countdown's on, man.
- Hey, man.

801
01:01:02,702 --> 01:01:05,580
One week left of your former life.
How you feeling?

802
01:01:05,705 --> 01:01:07,499
I feel pretty good, actually.

803
01:01:07,582 --> 01:01:10,752
I mean, I do get a little dizzy
if I think about it for too long, but...

804
01:01:10,877 --> 01:01:11,920
